#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Bionic Gunslinger"
msgstr "生化槍手"

#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Bionic Gunslinger"
msgstr "生化槍手"

#. ~ Profession (male Bionic Gunslinger) description
#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Lynched but not killed for a crime you didn't commit, you underwent "
"Augmentation surgery and hunted down those responsible with your trusty "
"revolver. now the apocolypse is here, and it's you, your cybernetics and "
"your gun against the world."
msgstr "你因未犯之罪被私刑處決卻未死，接受了改造手術，並用信賴的左輪手槍追捕了那些責任人。如今末日降臨，是你、你的義體與你的槍對抗整個世界。"

#. ~ Profession (female Bionic Gunslinger) description
#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
