msgstr "你因未犯之罪被私刑處決卻未死，接受了改造手術，並用信賴的左輪手槍追捕了那些責任人。如今末日降臨，是你、你的義體與你的槍對抗整個世界。"

#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Gunslinger"
msgstr "槍手"

#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Gunslinger"
msgstr "槍手"

#. ~ Profession (male Gunslinger) description
#: .\ProfessionsV1.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"before the cataclysm, you dedicated your life to wandering the western "
"reaches of the united states as a vigilante, killing modern criminals with "
"your old school revolver. now the apocolypse has arrived, and in this new "
"frontier your skills are needed more than ever."
msgstr ""
"大災變前，你畢生遊蕩在美國西部，作為一名義務警員，用老式左輪手槍消滅現代罪犯。如今末日降臨，在這片新邊疆，你的技能比以往任何時候都更加需要。"

